Example Usage: $identifiers=array(
'accession'=>'synonym',
'db_id'=>array(
'name'=>'SOFP'
)
);
$dbxref_object=chado_get_dbxref($identifiers);
 The above code selects the synonym database reference and returns the following object: $dbxref_object=stdClassObject(
[dbxref_id]=>2581
[accession]=>synonym
[description]=>
[version]=>
[db_db_id]=>49
[db_name]=>SOFP
[db_description]=>
[db_urlprefix]=>
[db_url]=>
);
